nodes.text: Shoo bread was a type of bread found on the planet Coruscant. By 29 BBY, the alien Yoda and Human Obi-Wan Kenobi, who were members of the Jedi Order on Coruscant, cooked shoo bread and wurr over a charcoal fire in Yoda's quarters of the Jedi Temple.
Shoo bread was mentioned in the 2000 novel Rogue Planet, written by Greg Bear.
